## Component Architecture

### Directory Structure

```
src/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router pages
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                 # shadcn/ui base components (customized)
│   ├── marketing/          # Tailark-based marketing sections
│   ├── animations/         # React Bits animation wrappers
│   └── icons/              # AnimateIcons + Lucide icon components
├── lib/
